---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const pageTitle = "官方公告｜香港共和國";
const pageDescription =
  "香港共和國政府官方公告：政策發布、新聞稿、官方聲明與公共通告。";
---

<BaseLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <section class="head">
    <div class="badge">公告中心</div>
    <h1>官方公告</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      本頁收錄政府部門與公共機構之官方發布，包括政策公告、新聞稿與官方聲明。內容按日期排序，
      以公開發布版本為準。
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="tools">
    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-title">查閱指引</div>
      <ul>
        <li>公告以發布日期排序（最新在前）。</li>
        <li>如出現版本差異，以政府正式登載版本為準。</li>
        <li>未經授權不得擅自更改、節錄或曲解公告內容。</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="tool-card">
      <div class="tool-title">分類</div>
      <div class="chips" aria-label="公告分類（展示用）">
        <span class="chip">政策通告</span>
        <span class="chip">新聞稿</span>
        <span class="chip">官方聲明</span>
        <span class="chip">市場與金融</span>
        <span class="chip">司法與法治</span>
        <span class="chip">公共服務</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="list">
    <div class="list-head">
      <h2>最新發布</h2>
      <div class="list-meta">共 3 則（示例）</div>
    </div>

    <article class="item">
      <div class="item-left">
        <time datetime="2043-07-15" class="date">2043-07-15</time>
        <span class="type">政策通告</span>
      </div>
      <div class="item-main">
        <h3 class="title">金融連續性與市場運作安排通告</h3>
        <p class="excerpt">
          概述市場結算、合約連續性及金融系統運作之安排，並列明相關執行機構與適用範圍。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="item-right">
        <a class="btn" href="/HKR/press">查閱</a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="item">
      <div class="item-left">
        <time datetime="2043-07-01" class="date">2043-07-01</time>
        <span class="type">官方聲明</span>
      </div>
      <div class="item-main">
        <h3 class="title">關於共和國制度運作之正式聲明</h3>
        <p class="excerpt">
          政府宣布憲政治理開始運作，公共機構依法履行職權，確保公共服務之持續性。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="item-right">
        <a class="btn" href="/HKR/press">查閱</a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="item">
      <div class="item-left">
        <time datetime="2043-08-03" class="date">2043-08-03</time>
        <span class="type">新聞稿</span>
      </div>
      <div class="item-main">
        <h3 class="title">司法行政架構調整與法院運作安排</h3>
        <p class="excerpt">
          交代法院行政與程序安排之最新措施，並重申司法獨立及正當程序保障。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="item-right">
        <a class="btn" href="/HKR/press">查閱</a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <div class="footnote">
      提示：下一步可接入內容系統，將每則公告獨立成一篇文件並提供永久連結與可檢索索引。
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .head {
      padding-top: 0.25rem;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.8px;
      color: #fff;
      background: #b80000;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.55rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .lead {
      color: #444;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      max-width: 58rem;
    }

    .tools {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .tool-card {
      border: 1px solid #e7e7e7;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: #fafafa;
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .tool-title {
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .tool-card ul {
      margin: 0.4rem 0 0;
      padding-left: 1.2rem;
      color: #333;
    }

    .tool-card li {
      margin: 0.4rem 0;
      color: #444;
    }

    .chips {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      margin-top: 0.35rem;
    }

    .chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0.22rem 0.55rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid #e7e7e7;
      background: #fff;
      color: #333;
      font-weight: 650;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
    }

    .list {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      border: 1px solid #e7e7e7;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: #fff;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .list-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1rem 1rem 0.75rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee;
      background: #fafafa;
    }

    .list-head h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .list-meta {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 170px 1fr 110px;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .item:last-of-type {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .item-left {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.35rem;
    }

    .date {
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #111;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .type {
      display: inline-flex;
      width: fit-content;
      padding: 0.18rem 0.5rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid #e7e7e7;
      background: #fafafa;
      color: #333;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }

    .title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2px;
    }

    .excerpt {
      margin: 0.35rem 0 0;
      color: #444;
    }

    .item-right {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 0.55rem 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 800;
      border: 1px solid #e7e7e7;
      background: #fff;
      color: #b80000;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: #f3f3f3;
    }

    .footnote {
      padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
      color: #666;
      background: #fafafa;
      border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .tools {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .item {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .item-right {
        justify-content: flex-start;
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
